hopobject.body: Three years edmunds.com vector logo "To date, EU policy to keep channels of communications open in Lebanon has allowed it to play a pro-active role in promoting political reform, social development and reconciliation in the country," said the group Conciliation Resources. "Today's development is disappointing for peace prospects in the region. Opportunities for dialogue should be encouraged rather than restrained, particularly at a time when Lebanon seems to be drawn ever more into the situation in Syria."
